Interface DisqueCommands<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - Key type.
    V - Value type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    DisqueClusterCommands<K,V>, DisqueJobCommands<K,V>, DisqueQueueCommands<K,V>, DisqueServerCommands<K,V>

    public interface DisqueCommands<K,V>
extends DisqueJobCommands<K,V>, DisqueQueueCommands<K,V>, DisqueServerCommands<K,V>, DisqueClusterCommands<K,V>
    Synchronous executed commands for Disque. This API is thread-safe.
    Author:
    Mark Paluch
